---
import Feature from '../../layouts/Feature.astro';
---

<Feature
  title="THEMES"
  subtitle="TOML color schemes with hot-reload and automatic light/dark switching."
>
  <h2>Custom Themes</h2>
  <p>Define your color scheme in TOML. Every color slot is configurable — foreground, background, cursor, selection, and all 16 ANSI colors. Place your theme file in the config directory and reference it by name.</p>

  <h2>Hot Reload</h2>
  <p>Theme changes take effect immediately. Edit your theme file, save, and see the results without restarting. Triggered automatically via file watcher or manually with <kbd>Ctrl+Shift+R</kbd>.</p>

  <h2>Light/Dark Auto-Switch</h2>
  <p>Configure separate light and dark themes in your config. ori-term follows your system appearance preference and switches instantly when you change your system setting.</p>

  <h2>Theme Conversion</h2>
  <p>Import existing themes from iTerm2, Ghostty, and base16 formats. Bring your theme collection with you.</p>
</Feature>
